    public class MaterialTreeItem
extends gwt.material.design.client.base.AbstractIconButton
implements gwt.material.design.client.base.HasImage, HasTreeItems
    MaterialTreeItem is a component that is needed by MaterialTree

    XML Namespace Declaration

     xmlns:ma='urn:import:gwt.material.design.addins.client'

    UiBinder Usage:

     &lt;-- Icon support -->
 <ma:tree.MaterialTreeItem text="Folder 1" iconType="FOLDER" />
 &lt;-- Image support -->
 <ma:tree.MaterialTreeItem text="Item 2.1" resource="{res.batman.png}" />
